description:
✴ Portrait of Beau


She's beauty. She's grace. She doesn't need a face.
She will be anything that you want her to be. She will do anything to be loved. The shapeshifter is the one and only came straight out of your dream.

✴[MAD GOD]✴ is an original dark fantasy series consist of blood and beautiful creatures portraying their life, their pride, and their attitude.
